Package: alz
Title: Criteria for Diagnosis and Staging of Alzheimer's Disease
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ramiro", "Magno", , "rmagno@pattern.institute", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5226-3441")),
    person("Pattern Institute", role = c("cph", "fnd"),
           comment = c("https://www.pattern.institute", ROR = "04jrgd746"))
  )
Description: 
  Tools for representing, organizing, and analyzing diagnostic and staging
  information related to Alzheimer's disease. Supports structured workflows for
  combining clinical, biological, and other staging variables in a consistent
  and reproducible manner. Intended for use in research, data harmonization,
  and interpretation of disease progression frameworks.
